		<div class="postbody">
			<div class="postrow has_after_content">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					&quot;DieselGate&quot; possible huge fall of VW Group?
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1841229">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<a href="http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34298259" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34298259</a><br />
<br />
The sheer impact of this on VW will be huge and it will bring questions to an already weak market in the US that is diesel powered cars.    They have already been the red headed stepchild of the US auto market even Electrics are seen with a better chance in the USDM.   My main question is wondering what this means for the future of VW because they fine potential here is not at all tiny slap on the wrist stuff its tens of billions,   And the damage to &quot;Clean Diesel&quot; marketing is even bigger.   It does not matter if other automakers are doing clean diesel the right way and not cheating,   Its a PR blow to the technology as a whole because consumers are not terribly intelligent.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
